Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: Matrix (>= 1.4), methods, Rcpp (>= 0.12.13)
Suggests: testthat, numDeriv, scales, knitr, xtable, dplyr
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen (>= 0.3.3.3.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
VignetteBuilder: knitr
SystemRequirements: C++11
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
NeedsCompilation: yes
